Title: House II: The Second Story
Writer: Fred Dekker (inspired by an original story by), Ethan Wiley
Actors: Arye Gross, Jonathan Stark, Royal Dano, Bill Maher
Plot: The new owner of a sinister house gets involved with reanimated corpses and demons searching for an ancient Aztec skull with magic powers.
Production: New World Pictures, Sean S. Cunningham Films
